<title>PHILIPPINES: RESEARCH ALERT - Cosmos rated a buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Cosmos rated a buy.</headline>
<dateline>MANILA 1996-10-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>BPI Securities recommended a buy on Cosmos Bottling Corp on Thursday, saying the firm's acquisition of a 173 million peso bottling facility will help increase its market share and boost earnings.</p>
<p>&quot;Cosmos is the only listed RFM subsidiary which had registered positive earnings growth as of the first half of 1996,&quot; analyst Spencer Yap said in a market brief.  </p>
<p>The new facility will increase Cosmos' bottling capacity by 30 percent every year, he said.</p>
<p>BPI Securities expects Cosmos to post profits of 214 million pesos by year-end and 310 million pesos by end-1997.</p>
